des: Hello, and welcome to Cisco Tips. This channel is meant for all those who want more out of life, for those who deserve more, for those who know they can achieve a higher potential. People are smart, so why do we make dumb decisions? It is not because we are dumb, it is because we have false and misleading information that leads us to make those dumb decisions. I want to help you change that. I want to arm you with empowering information in business and finance to ensure your financial freedom and a life of abundance. Tips on how simple mindset and habit changes can trigger massive change in your life. It is no secret, yet few can execute it. I am here to remind you daily of those things we tend to forget on our day to day routines. Let me coach you on money laws, business, finance and overall lifestyle. I will ensure you establish a solid foundation that no event, no person and no government can destroy. Success is your duty and if you have yet to reach your full potential, I am here to help you! So join me on this quest, all I ask is once you get to the level of success you seek, send me a message and share your story with me. There is nothing more satisfying to my heart than to know I helped a lost soul achieve greatness...
